title: George Strait - Troubadour
description:
The follow-up CD to George Strait\&#039;s platinum selling and CMA Album of the Year, IT JUST COMES NATURAL, is TROUBADOUR. George Strait truly is a modern day troubadour - now in his 28th year of making music,George continues to be an artist driven by his passion to make music of the highest quality. 
TROUBADOUR features the smash single \"I Saw God Today\".
